 630, \"to\": 653}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday morning\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Competing for GB have been by far the most memorable weeks of my career and I am extremely proud to get to do it one final time!\\\"\", \"from\": 675, \"to\": 805, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"GB\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 692}, {\"ngram\": \"the most memorable weeks\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 734}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 747}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray is set to play in the men's singles competition in Paris as well as in the men's doubles alongside fellow Briton Dan Evans.\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 937, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 807, \"end\": 813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.815931074548148e-55, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 865, \"end\": 870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999809006, \"rank\": 1.931241149109414e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 927, \"end\": 936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"score\": 0.9966766461228634, \"rank\": 0.0033344353859646567, \"text\": \"Dan Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the men's singles competition\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 861}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's doubles\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The tennis competition runs from July 27 until August 4 on the red clay at Roland Garros, home of the French Open.\", \"from\": 939, 